Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:14.77,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Myslíš si snáď,že ma porazí taký novo zazmluvnený amatér ako si ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.49,Kurokami,,0,0,0,,Ty jedna!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:16.91,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Eyes withholding sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.42,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}clearly reflects my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:23.42,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}as I endlessly drift and long for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:28.29,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}The answer that I was searching for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:29.32,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}was fusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:33.37,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}a path led to by pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:38.77,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Even if the absolute darkness compels me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.88,0:01:43.59,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}it has always brought me smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:48.51,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Because in order to protect the light,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:55.34,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}I can now become one with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.73,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}I received that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.47,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}scarce power
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:06.08,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}which can pierce through even wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:11.46,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}If we interact because we believe in each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.27,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}miracles will occur
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:16.28,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:21.83,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}We will also be able to see the truth one day.
