Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:56.65,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}melting this frozen body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:22:02.82,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}The memories awaken...
