Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:23.23,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}the bleak field,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:26.30,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}which has lost all sounds
